MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 670971587}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 107850cb441d34c6f85b55a756f40c69, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: '::'
  openedDrawer: {fileID: 7785607249659447786, guid: dab6503fbffd2614ca2fa12a896bba97, type: 3}
  closed_mail: {fileID: 1128545885}
  initialNoKey:
  - I threw some random stuff into this bottom drawer when I moved in and then when
    I closed the drawer it locked automatically. Just my luck.
  - "I don\u2019t have the key to open it. I wonder if I\u2019ll even be able to
    find it at this point. Everything is a mess."
  secondHasKey:
  - "Oh wow. I didn\u2019t actually expect that random key would actually unlock
    this. There seems to be something inside. Maybe I should take a look."
  initialHasKey:
  - I threw some random stuff into this bottom drawer when I moved in and then when
    I closed the drawer it locked automatically. Just my luck.
  - "I tried it on a whim, but I didn\u2019t actually expect that random key would
    actually unlock this. There seems to be something inside. "
  finalHasKey:
  - "It seems to be a\u2026 recipe? Might be from when I tried to get into cooking,
    I can barely even read the text, it\u2019s so old. "
  - "It seems to have a temperature on it though. Funny it's the only thing that\u2019s
    visible. "
