MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 908629698}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 541aa4e302e6e4455ada1333b4779918, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: '::'
  photoFramePeeking: {fileID: -1315762578906877138, guid: 55a10a305b3dd8949818970d6a6fdaf4, type: 3}
  zoomedPhoto: {fileID: 1088896999}
  dialogueBefore:
  - Oh, I forgot about this photo. We look just like a happy family in this photo.
  - "There seems to be something hidden behind our family photo. I don\u2019t remember
    putting anything here."
  dialogueAfter:
  - "Ah, Margarite. I was so ashamed I forgot I hid this here. We had\u2026 a unique
    connection. "
  - "Oh? There\u2019s scribbles on the photo. It reminds me of the invisible ink
    she taught me to make. She would often leave secret notes using it."
  - 'I remember it was temperature activated, and we would put it in the oven to
    reveal the secret text. That sounds ridiculous now. Back then, we were young
    and foolish. '
  - "I don\u2019t even remember what the temperature was. Maybe I wrote it down somewhere\u2026"
