  turningOvenOn:
  - "I\u2019ll put the photo in the oven and hopefully it\u2019ll still work. The
    ink is old so I\u2019m not even sure if this will work."
  revealingText:
  - "It worked! \u2026. But,  I was\u2026 not ready to see that. It just reminds
    me of my shameful past."
  - "Ugh, this is giving me a headache. I\u2019ll pretend this never happened."
