  - A nice assortment of kitchen tools. Spatula, spoon, scissors. Funny, makes it
    seem like I really cook.
  gotMail:
  - "Perfect. I\u2019ll use these scissors here to open up that mail I found. I think
    I left it in my closet."
  gotPhoto:
  - Perfect. I can cutout that bastard with these scissors.
  gotPhotoAndMail:
  - Just what I needed! I can use these to open up that mail and cut that bastard
    out from the photo. I just need to go back to where I found them.
